 
 
 
 
 
The Idioms and Proverbial Phrases 
He left her after he got what he wanted from her./She accomplished her desire 
to travel the world./After they accomplished their needs, the employees aban­
doned their jobs and started their own businesses./He died without achieving 
his goals in life. 
